title: Mondays with Matt & J - Setting 2020 Non-Negotiables
description:
This marks the first episode of Mondays with Matt & J on the She Podcast!
We talked about setting non-negotiables for our family to create healthy boundaries and practices to help us flourish this year.
author: matt@jordanleedooley.com (Jordan Lee Dooley)
